，表示裹心的祝贺，祝贺他们在抗击美国的斗争中取得的这些重大胜利。","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a75dd3f475"},{"id":"b67ace77ca","type":"paragraph","text":"正如苏军在与第一流武装的德军作战取得了现代战争的丰富经验，并变成为装备精良的现代化军队一样，在反击现代化和装备精良的美车的战争中，中国军队无疑地也将取得现代战争的主富经验，其本身也将变成完全现代化的、装备精良的、威力强大的军队。","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a75dd3f475"},{"id":"7d9a461066","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你们取得进一步的胜利","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a75dd3f475"},{"id":"d2a5bc18ad","type":"paragraph","text":"菲利波夫","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a75dd3f475"},{"id":"3716ebe0bf","type":"paragraph","text":"1950年12月1日”","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a75dd3f475"},{"id":"41c226895a","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》《朝鲜战争：俄国档案馆的解密文件（中册）第633页","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a75dd3f475"},{"id":"a82fa297c2","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷九第108页","index":13,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a75dd3f475"}],"page":{"id":"8e567f397c","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"a75dd3f475","start":2742,"end":2742}}}},"__N_SSG":true}